Assignment - 1 

Q. 1: Create an HTML Form containing a user registration form with having fields like username, password, re-type password, first name, last name, email address, mobile number, submit button, reset button.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .form-container {
        width: 80%;
        max-width: 300px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .form-field {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .form-field label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .form-field input {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .form-field input[type="submit"],
      .form-field input[type="reset"] {
        width: auto;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 4px 2px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .form-field input[type="submit"]:hover,
      .form-field input[type="reset"]:hover {
        background-color: #45a049;
      }

      /* Responsive styles */
      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .form-container {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="form-container">
      <form>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="username">Username</label>
          <input type="text" id="username" name="username" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="password">Password</label>
          <input type="password" id="password" name="password" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="retype-password">Re-type Password</label>
          <input type="password" id="retype-password" name="retype-password" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="first-name">First Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="first-name" name="first-name" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="last-name">Last Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="last-name" name="last-name" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="mobile-number">Mobile Number</label>
          <input type="tel" id="mobile-number" name="mobile-number" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
          <input type="reset" value="Reset" />
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

Q. 2: Creat an HTML page containing a table having two rows and two columns. In each cell, you are supposed to embed YouTube Videos on HTML tutorial. 
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>HTML Tutorial Videos</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <td>
