Q. 3: Creat an HTML page containing at least an image, an embedded audio/video file, and user feedback form (fields: username, feedback, date, submit button)
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Sample Page</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to the Sample Page</h1>

    <img src="path_to_your_image.jpg" alt="Sample Image" />

    <audio controls>
      <source src="path_to_your_audio.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" />
      Your browser does not support the audio element.
    </audio>

    <video width="320" height="240" controls>
      <source src="path_to_your_video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>

    <form action="submit_form.php" method="post">
      <label for="username">Username:</label><br />
      <input type="text" id="username" name="username" /><br />
      <label for="feedback">Feedback:</label><br />
      <textarea id="feedback" name="feedback"></textarea><br />
      <label for="date">Date:</label><br />
      <input type="date" id="date" name="date" /><br />
      <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
    </form>
  </body>
</html>

